_:N870dab7870454aa19c51ec38b4274608 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Steve Reed OBE was appointed Secretary of State for Housing, Communities and Local Government on 5 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>He was previously Secretary of State for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs from 5 July 2024 to 5 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>He was elected as the MP for Streatham and Croydon North in July 2024.</p>\n" .
